sections.text:
86-1051.Public safety agency, defined.

Public safety agency means an agency which provides emergency services.

SourceLaws 2016, LB938, § 21;R.S.1943, (2024), § 86-1021;Laws 2025, LB362, § 33.Effective Date: September 3, 2025
